data.title: The Blue Lamp Reel/Liz Doherty
data.meta_description: I was listening/watching the Celtic Colours live stream and was absolutely amazed by Liz Doherty’s set.   She played a tune called “The Blue Lamp”.   It is also on her Quare Imagination album.   I can’t seem to find any sheet music under that name.
